OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772741480
OL,3,C'Half of me has gone': Widow's grief
OL,4,Cand #160k fine for firm for workplace
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FA Co Londonderry woman whose husband
OL,8,Fwas crushed to death while at work in
OL,9,F2023 says that the #160,000 fine
OL,10,Fhanded to his employer is a 'drop in
OL,11,Fthe ocean' compared to her grief.
OL,13,FColin Thomas died in April 2023 at the
OL,14,Fmanufacturing company Tobermore in
OL,15,Fwhat the Health and Safety Executive
OL,16,Fdescribed as a "tragic and wholly
OL,17,Fpreventable" incident.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772741480
OL,3,C'Half of me has gone': Widow's grief
OL,4,Cand #160k fine for firm for workplace
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FIn February 2025, Tobermore pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to a single health and safety
OL,9,Foffence of failing to ensure the
OL,10,Fhealth, safety and welfare of its
OL,11,Femployees.
OL,13,FThe company owner told UTV Colin's
OL,14,Fdeath had a profound effect on those
OL,15,Fassociated with the firm and offered
OL,16,Fit's sincere condolences. David
OL,17,FHenderson acknowledged his death
OL,18,Fshould not have happened.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772741480
OL,3,C'Half of me has gone': Widow's grief
OL,4,Cand #160k fine for firm for workplace
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FColin's wife Karen described her loss
OL,8,Fas 'unimaginable' saying she would not
OL,9,Fwish it on anybody.
OL,11,F"Because it was just the two of us, I
OL,12,Fjust feel half of me has gone since
OL,13,Fthe night it happened. I just want to
OL,14,Fremember him going out the door that
OL,15,Fnight to go to work," she told UTV in
OL,16,Fher first interview since Colin's
OL,17,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772741480
OL,3,C'Half of me has gone': Widow's grief
OL,4,Cand #160k fine for firm for workplace
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"We always were standing in the hall
OL,8,Fand he was heading out at 5:30 and
OL,9,Fevery night we told each other that we
OL,10,Floved each other and my last words to
OL,11,Fhim every time are, you take care.
OL,13,F"No one should be getting that rap at
OL,14,Ftheir bedroom window at 3:45 in the
OL,15,Fmorning," she said, recollecting the
OL,16,Fnight she found out that Colin had
OL,17,Fdied.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772741480
OL,3,C'Half of me has gone': Widow's grief
OL,4,Cand #160k fine for firm for workplace
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"It was horrific but I knew. I knew
OL,8,Fwhen I walked down the hall and saw
OL,9,Fthe policeman standing. I couldn't
OL,10,Feven get the key in the door."
OL,12,FColin is one of a number of people to
OL,13,Fhave died in workplace related
OL,14,Faccidents, with 68 fatalities recorded
OL,15,Fby the Health and Safety Executive NI
OL,16,F(HSENI) between 2020 and 2025.
OL,18,FA total of 1,146 people have also been
OL,19,Fseriously injured in workplace related
OL,20,Faccidents in that same time period.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772741480
OL,3,C'Half of me has gone': Widow's grief
OL,4,Cand #160k fine for firm for workplace
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"Any employee, doesn't matter where
OL,8,Fthey work or what department," Karen
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"They should be going out to their
OL,12,Fwork, doing a day's work, and coming
OL,13,Fback to their family.
OL,15,FKaren says she has not received an
OL,16,Fapology from Tobermore since Colin's
OL,17,Fdeath - even though they pleaded
OL,18,Fguilty in court and have since been
OL,19,Fconvicted..
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772741480
OL,3,C'Half of me has gone': Widow's grief
OL,4,Cand #160k fine for firm for workplace
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"I saw them in court that Thursday and
OL,8,Fthat was the first I had seen senior
OL,9,Fmanagement or heard from senior
OL,10,Fmanagement from the day of Colin's
OL,11,Ffuneral."
OL,13,FIn response, David Henderson, chairman
OL,14,Fand owner of Tobermore told UTV in a
OL,15,Fstatement: "Colin's life was lost in
OL,16,Fcircumstances that should never have
OL,17,Fhappened.
OL,19,F"We acknowledge that again today and
OL,20,Freiterate our sincere condolences and
OL,21,Fdeep sorrow for his loss.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772741480
OL,3,C'Half of me has gone': Widow's grief
OL,4,Cand #160k fine for firm for workplace
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"Our thoughts are with his wife,
OL,8,FKaren, and his wider family.
OL,10,F"Everyone associated with Tobermore
OL,11,Fhas been deeply affected by Colin's
OL,12,Fdeath and continues to be so."
OL,14,FWorkplaces such as Tobermore are often
OL,15,Fsubject to workplace inspections by
OL,16,FHSENI - most of these are unannounced,
OL,17,Fwith the employer not given advance
OL,18,Fnotice.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772741480
OL,3,C'Half of me has gone': Widow's grief
OL,4,Cand #160k fine for firm for workplace
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FHowever, Karen is frustrated that some
OL,8,Finspections are pre-organised in
OL,9,Fadvance.
OL,11,F"It gives the employer the opportunity
OL,12,Fto tidy up and make sure all the I's
OL,13,Fare dotted and the T's are crossed.
OL,15,F"It might as well not happen. They
OL,16,Fneed to go in unannounced," Karen said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772741480
OL,3,C'Half of me has gone': Widow's grief
OL,4,Cand #160k fine for firm for workplace
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FIn response, a spokesperson for HSENI
OL,8,Fsaid: "The organisation does not have
OL,9,Fa policy of announced visits, however
OL,10,Fon some occasions it may necessitate a
OL,11,Fpre-arranged meeting time should there
OL,12,Fbe a need to speak to someone in
OL,13,Fparticular,
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772741480
OL,3,C'Half of me has gone': Widow's grief
OL,4,Cand #160k fine for firm for workplace
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"Alongside inspections, and as part of
OL,8,FHSENI's wider regulatory role, the
OL,9,Forganisation carries out
OL,10,Finvestigations, responds to concerns,
OL,11,Fissues enforcement notices and makes
OL,12,Frecommendations to the Public
OL,13,FProsecution Service for Northern
OL,14,FIreland following workplace
OL,15,Finvestigations.
OL,17,F"Through its role in providing
OL,18,Finformation and advice, HSENI also
OL,19,Faims to help improve understanding and
OL,20,Fcompliance with health and safety
OL,21,Frequirements.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772741480
OL,3,C'Half of me has gone': Widow's grief
OL,4,Cand #160k fine for firm for workplace
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"As Mr Thomas' death has shown, when
OL,8,Femployers fail to meet that their
OL,9,Flegal responsibilities, HSENI will
OL,10,Ftake the appropriate enforcement
OL,11,Faction. We hope that the wider
OL,12,Findustry reflects on the lessons from
OL,13,Fthis tragedy so that similar incidents
OL,14,Fcan be prevented in the future."
OL,16,FWhilst speaking to UTV, Karen was keen
OL,17,Fto thank those who have rallied around
OL,18,Fher since Colin's death.
OL,26,@vD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772741480
OL,3,C'Half of me has gone': Widow's grief
OL,4,Cand #160k fine for firm for workplace
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"They have been amazing. My family and
OL,8,Ffriends and neighbors are amazing. A
OL,9,Fbig, big thank you," she said.
OL,11,F"I would give up everything I own to
OL,12,Fhave him back again with me - it's
OL,13,Funbearable."JCatch up with the latest
OL,14,FUTV Live on ITVX
OL,16,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,17,Fhere.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/13
